{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-chenfeng-010__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-chenfeng-010", "source_id": "guofeng-chenfeng-010__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·陳風·010.1", "text_original": "彼澤之陂，有蒲與荷。有美一人，傷如之何。寤寐無為，涕泗滂沱。", "text_normalized": "彼澤之陂，有蒲與荷。有美一人，傷如之何。寤寐無為，涕泗滂沱。", "notes": "澤陂 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-chenfeng-010__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-chenfeng-010", "source_id": "guofeng-chenfeng-010__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·陳風·010.2", "text_original": "彼澤之陂，有蒲與蕑。有美一人，碩大且卷。寤寐無為，中心悁悁。", "text_normalized": "彼澤之陂，有蒲與蕑。有美一人，碩大且卷。寤寐無為，中心悁悁。", "notes": "澤陂 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-chenfeng-010__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-chenfeng-010", "source_id": "guofeng-chenfeng-010__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·陳風·010.3", "text_original": "彼澤之陂，有蒲菡萏。有美一人，碩大且儼。寤寐無為，輾轉伏枕。", "text_normalized": "彼澤之陂，有蒲菡萏。有美一人，碩大且儼。寤寐無為，輾轉伏枕。", "notes": "澤陂 Chinese stanza 3."}
